
## ============================================
## Bagua World Worker — API Test Suite
## ============================================
## Toggle between local and production:
# @host = http://localhost:8787
@host = https://api.app.bagua.world

## ============================================
## Auth
## ============================================

### Get Nonce
POST {{host}}/open/nonce
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Login (SIWE — requires valid wallet signature)
POST {{host}}/open/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "YOUR_SIWE_MESSAGE",
    "signature": "YOUR_WALLET_SIGNATURE"
}

###

### Check Session
POST {{host}}/open/me
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Generate Transfer Token (QR login)
POST {{host}}/open/me2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ttlDays": 90
}

###

### Logout
POST {{host}}/open/logout
Content-Type: application/json

###

## ============================================
## Palace Service (gRPC/Connect)
## ============================================

### Palace Sync
POST {{host}}/BaguaPalaceService/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ego": "",
    "clientNonce": ""
}

###

### Palace Handle Command (example: save hook)
POST {{host}}/BaguaPalaceService/handleCmd
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ego": "",
    "clientNonce": "",
    "cmdType": 1,
    "cmdVersion": 1,
    "data": {}
}

###

## ============================================
## Cache Management
## ============================================

### Delete Ego Cache
DELETE {{host}}/api/cache/ego/0x2AE47ccC63878d892bf2675a9d3b497DDD9eb82F